    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a respectable shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some light surface scratches and a few minor stone chips on the front bumper. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only standard wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffing on the door sills. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a well-maintained vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning, mint-condition beauty! This car is truly in showroom state, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that feels brand new. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, offering a driving experience that is as smooth and refined as the day it was first built. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and performs like a dream!",
      "price": 48500.0,
